<div class="wordle-rules">
    <h1>Wordle Rules</h1>
    
    <h2>Objective</h2>
    <p>Guess the hidden five-letter word within six attempts.</p>
    
    <h2>How to Play</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">1. Enter a valid five-letter word as your guess.</div>
      <div class="step">2. Press the "Enter" button to submit your guess.</div>
      <div class="step">3. Receive feedback on your guess:</div>
      <div class="feedback">
        <div><span style="border-color: green; border-width: 5px;"></span>: The letter is in the correct position.</div>
        <div><span style="border-color: orange; border-width: 5px;"></span>: The letter is in the word but in the wrong position.</div>
        <div><span style="border-color: gray; border-width: 5px;"></span>: The letter is not in the word at all.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">4. Use the feedback to refine your next guess.</div>
      <div class="step">5. Continue guessing until you find the correct word or use all six attempts.</div>
    </div>
  
    <h2>Tips</h2>
    <div class="tips">
      <div class="tip">• Start with common five-letter words.</div>
      <div class="tip">• Pay attention to the feedback to narrow down possibilities.</div>
    </div>
  
    <h2>Enjoy the Challenge!</h2>
    <p>Have fun and test your vocabulary skills!</p>
  </div>
  
